"content": "<style>\nh1.thlex-title { font-size: 1.3em; margin: 0 0 0.4em; }\n.thlex-key { color: #888; font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: normal; margin-right: 0.4em; }\nnav.thlex-index { margin: 0.5em 0 0.75em; }\nnav.thlex-index ul { margin: 0; padding-left: 1.2em; }\nnav.thlex-index li { margin: 0.15em 0; font-size: 0.95em; }\n.thlex-section { margin: 0.6em 0; }\nh2.thlex-heading { font-size: 1em; margin: 0.5em 0 0.2em; }\nh3.thlex-subheading { font-size: 0.95em; font-weight: normal; font-style: italic; margin: 0.2em 0; }\n.thlex-language-sets { margin: 0.3em 0 0.3em 1em; }\n.thlex-language-set { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 0.75em; border-left: 3px solid #e0e0e0; }\n.thlex-language { font-size: 0.8em; color: #888; margin-right: 0.4em; }\n.thlex-lemma { font-weight: bold; font-family: serif; }\n.thlex-translit { color: #555; font-style: italic; font-size: 0.9em; margin-left: 0.3em; }\n.thlex-refs { font-size: 0.85em; color: #444; margin-top: 0.15em; }\n.thlex-paragraphs p { margin: 0.35em 0; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.5; }\n.thlex-image { margin: 0.5em 0; display: block; }\n.thlex-image img { max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: block; }\nfigcaption.thlex-caption { font-size: 0.85em; color: #555; font-style: italic; margin-top: 0.2em; }\n.thlex-abbr { border-bottom: 1px dotted #888; cursor: help; }\n.thlex-xref { color: #1a5fb4; }\nspan[data-bnType=\"bibleReference\"] { color: #1a5fb4; }\ntable.thlex-table { border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 0.9em; margin: 0.5em 0; }\ntable.thlex-table td { padding: 0.2em 0.6em; vertical-align: top; border: 1px solid #ddd; }\ntable.thlex-table tr:first-child td { font-weight: bold; background: #f5f5f5; }\nul.thlex-index-list { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.6; }\nul.thlex-index-list ul { margin: 0.1em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; }\n.thlex-index-key { font-weight: bold; font-style: italic; }\n</style><h1 class=\"thlex-title\" id=\"REALIA:1.3.3\"><span class=\"thlex-key\">1.3.3</span> 标题：鱼叉（fishing spear, harpoon）</h1><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">经文出处</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-sets\">\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">来：חָח, חוֹחַ</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：chach, choach)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs19:28\">2KI 19:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr33:11\">2CH 33:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job40:26\">JOB 40:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa37:29\">ISA 37:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek19:4\">EZK 19:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek19:9\">EZK 19:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek29:4\">EZK 29:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek38:4\">EZK 38:4</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">来：חַכָּה</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：chakah)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job40:25\">JOB 40:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa19:8\">ISA 19:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab1:15\">HAB 1:15</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">来：מַסָּע</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：masa‘)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job41:18\">JOB 41:18</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">来：שֻׂכָּה</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：sukah)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job40:31\">JOB 40:31</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">来：צִלְצָל</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：tsiltsal)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job40:31\">JOB 40:31</a></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">描述</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>\n            <figure class=\"thlex-image\"><img class=\"thlex-img\" src=\"images/WEB-0338_fishing_spear.jpg\" alt=\"捕鱼叉的尖头（青铜或铜合金，埃及，约公元前1550-1070年）\"><figcaption class=\"thlex-caption\">捕鱼叉的尖头（青铜或铜合金，埃及，约公元前1550–1070年） (Metropolitan Museum of Art, Public domain)</figcaption></figure>鱼叉是一根约有一人高的木杆，一端套上用金属或骨头做成的、带倒刺的尖头，另一端很可能会系上一根绳子，这样投掷者就可以把投出去的鱼叉再拉回来。</p>\n<hr/>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">用途</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>渔夫瞄准鱼或其他水生动物，然后用力掷出鱼叉。倒钩可防止叉头从猎物身上脱落。连接在叉头另一端的绳子使投掷者能够快速收回鱼叉，准备再次投掷，或者防止受伤的猎物拖着鱼叉游走。</p>\n<hr/>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">翻译</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>《〈约伯记〉手册》（<em>A Handbook on The Book of Job</em> ）指出，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job40:26\">JOB 40:26</a> （《和》41:2）中的希伯来文<em>choach</em> 指的是一种钩子，但这个钩子“比前一节中的鱼钩大得多”（第752页）。这个词最常出现在与对待囚犯有关的描述中，这也是<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job40:25\">JOB 40:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job40:31\">JOB 40:31</a> （《和》41:1，7）用在力威亚探身上的涵义。</p>\n<p>在<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job41:18\">JOB 41:18</a> （《和》41:26），希伯来文<em>masa&#x27;</em> 的含义并不确定。从上下文来看，很明显这是一种用来捕猎大型动物的武器，也许是投掷武器。希伯来文本在这节经文的末尾有三个单词，<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Contemporary English Version\">CEV</abbr> 将这三个词语简单地统译为“spear”（“矛”）。<em>Masa&#x27;</em> 一词最常译为“飞镖”（“dart”；<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Revised Standard Version (1952)\">RSV</abbr> 、<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"New International Version (1984)\">NIV</abbr> 、<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"New American Standard Bible\">NASB</abbr> 、<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"New Century Version\">NCV</abbr> 、<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Revised English Bible (1989)\">REB</abbr> ），不过也有译本译为“飞弹”（“missile”；<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"New Jewish Publication Society Version\">NJPSV</abbr> ）、“投枪”（“javelin”；<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"New Jerusalem Bible (1985)\">NJB</abbr> ）和“箭”（“arrow”；<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Good News Translation (1992)\">GNT</abbr> ）。尽管英文单词“dart”（“飞镖”）在现代译本中十分常见，但是对那些并不熟悉《钦定本圣经》或莎士比亚英文的现代读者来说，这个词仅仅指在游戏中投掷的小而尖的羽毛飞镖。</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
